snippet.textDisplay: @Call of Duty Can you make it so people can tie for 3rd in Free for all? Make it so the outcome is decided only by the number of kills the player has. Players can tie for 1st even though one has less deaths  than the other but when it comes to 3rd, the number of deaths decides who get the 3rd place or not. To think you have come in 3rd only to see Defeat because you had a few more deaths but the same number of kills is a slap to the face. I'm sorry I'm sick of that slap to the face. Letting players tie for 3rd would keep more players happy and also keep them playing the game. Please make this happen through an update. Please keep things fair for all players.
snippet.textOriginal: @Call of Duty Can you make it so people can tie for 3rd in Free for all? Make it so the outcome is decided only by the number of kills the player has. Players can tie for 1st even though one has less deaths  than the other but when it comes to 3rd, the number of deaths decides who get the 3rd place or not. To think you have come in 3rd only to see Defeat because you had a few more deaths but the same number of kills is a slap to the face. I'm sorry I'm sick of that slap to the face. Letting players tie for 3rd would keep more players happy and also keep them playing the game. Please make this happen through an update. Please keep things fair for all players.
